# Local API key files — never commit these.
# Pattern-matched AND named explicitly (belt + braces) so a rename
# can't accidentally un-ignore a live key. NOTE: this repo lives under
# a OneDrive-synced path — gitignore protects the REPO, not the local
# disk. Keep the plaintext key files OUT of cloud-synced folders, or
# move them to an OS keychain / Vercel env, for real at-rest security.
*Key.txt
*key.txt
*secret*.txt
*.pem
Clade PAYG Key.txt
OpenAI key.txt
*.key
keys/
# TimeBack roster snapshots (PII — pasted into admin UI then deleted)
timeback-grade-sync-*.json
caliper-sample-event*.json
# RAG experiment artifacts (raw text + generated outputs — re-generatable)
scripts/.peter-rabbit-raw.txt
scripts/rag-experiment-output.*
# TTS pre-warm resume index (regeneratable — just a list of warmed Blob clips)
prewarm.progress
package-lock.json
.env.prod.local
repair-tts.report*.txt
resynth.progress
